&lt;h2 class="accordion-header"&gt;
  &lt;button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne"&gt;
    1. Geospatial Consulting
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#servicesAccordion"&gt;
  &lt;div class="accordion-body"&gt;
    We offer tailored strategies for site-specific and regional environmental challenges.
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Landscape Analysis:&lt;/strong&gt; Assessing spatial patterns and environmental change over time.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Environmental Risk Assessment:&lt;/strong&gt; Leveraging spatial intelligence to mitigate operational risks.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Strategy:&lt;/strong&gt; Advising on the integration of geospatial technology into your existing workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 class="accordion-header"&gt;
  &lt;button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"&gt;
    2. Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#servicesAccordion"&gt;
  &lt;div class="accordion-body"&gt;
    Spatial data is only as good as its foundation. We ensure your datasets are robust and analysis-ready.
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Integration:&lt;/strong&gt; Merging disparate spatial and non-spatial environmental datasets.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cleaning & Quality Control:&lt;/strong&gt; Systematic removal of errors, noise, and inconsistencies in spatial features.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preprocessing Pipelines:&lt;/strong&gt; Developing reproducible workflows for automated data preparation.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 class="accordion-header"&gt;
  &lt;button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree"&gt;
    3. Professional Training & Capacity Building
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#servicesAccordion"&gt;
  &lt;div class="accordion-body"&gt;
    We empower your team to handle complex spatial challenges with confidence.
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spatial Statistics:&lt;/strong&gt; Hands-on workshops covering modern methods for point pattern analysis, spatial regression, and interpolation.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ecological Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Technical courses on predictive modeling, habitat suitability, and species distribution.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Geospatial Application:&lt;/strong&gt; Custom training in R/Python for GIS, advanced raster analysis, and automated mapping.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h2 class="accordion-header"&gt;
  &lt;button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour"&gt;
    4. Analytical Support
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#servicesAccordion"&gt;
  &lt;div class="accordion-body"&gt;
    Beyond data preparation, we offer deep-dive analytical services for specialized research.
    &lt;ul&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Statistical Modeling:&lt;/strong&gt; Building custom models to address unique ecological questions.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Visualization:&lt;/strong&gt; Creating high-impact, data-driven visualizations for reporting and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
      &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Code Review & Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Refining your existing spatial scripts for speed, scalability, and reproducibility.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

Select an application below to view interactive dashboards, project methodology, and system architectures.
&lt;div class=“project-grid”&gt;





Automated Mangrove Monitoring







Habitat Suitability Analytics







Spatial Decision Support


